ZH: 我今天忘记带遮阳伞出门了。
EN: I forgot to bring my umbrella for sunshades today.

ZH: 妈妈给我买了一把漂亮的遮阳伞。
EN: Mom bought me a beautiful sun umbrella.

ZH: 明天天气预报说会有大太阳，还是要带上遮阳伞。
EN: The weather forecast says there will be a big sun tomorrow, so bring your sun umbrella.

ZH: 在炎热的夏天，大家都会用遮阳伞避免晒伤。
EN: In the hot summer, everyone will use a sun umbrella to avoid getting sunburned.

ZH: 他拿着遮阳伞，走在阳光下，看起来非常酷。
EN: He walked under the sun with an umbrella and looked very cool.

ZH: 遮阳伞可以阻挡阳光，保护皮肤不受损伤。
EN: Sun umbrellas can block sunlight and protect the skin from damage.

ZH: 这个遮阳伞的颜色很亮，很容易被人注意到。
EN: The color of this sun umbrella is bright and easily caught people's attention.

ZH: 我们找到一片树荫坐下来，不再需要遮阳伞了。
EN: We found a spot in the shade and no longer needed the sun umbrella.

ZH: 遮阳伞帮助我们在户外活动时保持清凉和舒适。
EN: Sun umbrellas help us stay cool and comfortable during outdoor activities.

ZH: 她用遮阳伞遮住了头发，以免晒伤。
EN: She used the sun umbrella to cover her hair to avoid getting sunburned.

ZH: 我的遮阳伞被风刮破了，需要修理一下。
EN: My sun umbrella was torn by the wind and needs to be repaired.

ZH: 每个人都应该有一把遮阳伞，以应对炎热的天气。
EN: Everyone should have a sun umbrella to cope with the hot weather.

ZH: 遮阳伞不仅可以用来遮阳，还可以用来遮雨。
EN: Sun umbrellas can be used not only for shading but also for sheltering from rain.

ZH: 这把遮阳伞设计得很小巧，容易携带。
EN: This sun umbrella is designed to be small and easy to carry.

ZH: 我觉得这把遮阳伞的款式很时尚。
EN: I think the design of this sun umbrella is very fashionable.

ZH: 在海边玩耍时，一个好用的遮阳伞是必备的。
EN: A good sun umbrella is essential when playing at the beach.

ZH: 汽车里的遮阳伞可以帮助人们避免阳光直射。
EN: The sunshade in the car can help people avoid direct sunlight.

ZH: 这个遮阳伞可以调节高度，适应不同需求。
EN: This sun umbrella can be adjusted in height to meet different needs.

ZH: 这个遮阳伞的把手很舒服，握起来不累。
EN: The handle of this sun umbrella is very comfortable, not tiring to hold.

ZH: 阳台上摆放一把遮阳伞，可以增加户外空间的舒适度。
EN: Placing a sun umbrella on the balcony can increase the comfort of outdoor space.
